https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null 'Gurdun' was the name given to the storm which wreaked havoc on the south of Sweden, its landscape and its people, on January 8, 2005. This documentary shows the destruction and the people most affected by it, and tries to come to terms with the extent of the damage. Efter Stormen
